snippet.title: Cube World Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Cube World is coming to Steam on 30 September 2019!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1128000/Cube_World/

The closed beta for all alpha owners starts on 23 September 2019!

Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/wol_lay
